&lt;p&gt;In this role, you will leverage your trading expertise and client relationships to originate and execute OTC trades across spot and derivatives markets. You will play a key role in expanding GSR’s OTC franchise by developing and executing client flow, managing risk, and delivering best-in-class execution.&lt;/p&gt;
