&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Originate, price, and execute OTC trades across crypto spot and derivatives markets.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and grow client relationships, driving trading volumes and revenue generation.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain and expand relationships with institutional clients, funds, brokers, and HNW counterparties.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage risk and exposure in real time, ensuring adherence to internal risk frameworks.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor market conditions, liquidity, and pricing to optimize execution and profitability.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with internal trading, quant, and technology teams to enhance pricing, execution, and client offering.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to the expansion of GSR’s OTC franchise across regions and products.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Profile&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience in crypto OTC trading or sales trading, with a strong track record of revenue generation.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Consistent track record of generating and growing client flow within crypto OTC or institutional trading environments.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep understanding of crypto markets, including spot, derivatives, and liquidity dynamics.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong commercial acumen with the ability to identify and execute profitable trading opportunities.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
